\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我同佢講完香港樓價個朋友仲話 &quot; Hong Kong is Hell&quot;<br />\n佢個老闆係比佢一個人做晒成單project. 由設計到試行都係比佢做<br />\n佢做風力發電果D風車葉, 特登去機場拎支70-80m 既風車葉用TESTING整斷佢睇下強度夠唔夠, <br />\n反觀亞洲區我地呢D所謂專業人士, 有份做, 冇份睇, 比人當狗咁洗真係好妒忌.<br />\n<br />\n仲話唔洗OT, 一係咪CLAIM佢OT錢, 唔OT冇得迫, 因為法例保障左員工.<br />\n<br />\n仲有仲有, 買樓佢話70萬已經有2層House (2500ft 左右) , 50萬就有空地 (睇地區)"},{"pid":"834b722ca8d6dc053f5ea1cb1902210ae88877ee","tid":187821,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T02:33:57.000Z","msg":"德國"},{"pid":"d6da82b86e72036d6af91bad32c47c350de34f96","tid":187821,"uid":52594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T09:29:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n意見好一面倒"},{"pid":"8604f614ea50161b99965df2a511397be2c6ddcb","tid":187821,"uid":52824,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T09:33:19.000Z","msg":"有留意時事都知日本打工仔好撚慘<br />\n一面倒都正常啦"},{"pid":"e214d1faf3b5e488f9b23b5b72aeb1dcb4e71ae1","tid":187821,"uid":103967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T09:39:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"122708abd7e282bdeec2722d5dbb4e83743d40e5","tid":187821,"uid":54431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T10:20:29.000Z","msg":"有能力都唔會番香港真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}